(FileStreamBot - Full Project Working Explanation) Tj
T* (===============================================) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1\) What this project is) Tj
T* (-----------------------) Tj
T* (FileStreamBot is a Telegram bot plus a small web server.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Its job is:) Tj
T* (- receive media files from Telegram users or channels) Tj
T* (- save file metadata in MongoDB) Tj
T* (- generate stream/download links) Tj
T* (- serve the actual file bytes from Telegram directly through a web URL) Tj
T* (- avoid storing big files permanently on the server) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (So the server mainly stores metadata, not the full media file.) Tj
T* (The real media still comes from Telegram when someone opens the web link.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (2\) Main idea in one line) Tj
T* (------------------------) Tj
T* (Telegram file -> bot reads file info -> metadata saved in MongoDB -> web link created -> ) Tj
T* (aiohttp route streams bytes from Telegram to browser/user.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
